[I] Perl module Finance::Quote

[T] Finance::Quote provides access to time-delayed stockquotes from a
[T] number of sources. After you've installed the pacakage, try
[T] 'perldoc Finance::Quote' for full information. Alternatively,
[T] you can 'perldoc lib/Finance/Quote.pm' before the install.

